title: 10x FY17 Impact Report
subtitle: 10x FY17 Impact Report
excerpt: FY17 brings us our first-ever impact report as a burgeoning investment program. Highlights in this report include our early iterations on the funding amounts for each phase, a detailed breakdown of the number of projects we supported and their outcomes, and a snapshot of a few projects, including: _Notification Services_ and _Cloud Marketplace_.
